title: Don't Regret Your Life
itunes:title: Don't Regret Your Life
description:
Episode 442 -  The #1 regret of the dying was "I wish I lived a life that was true to myself." When you look back on your life, will it be unfulfilled dreams or will you look back with pride, knowing that you put everything that you could into it? Let's dive into regret on this episode because the only thing worse than the pain of hard work is the pain of regret.
